  "description": "A close-up view of a rocky coastline featuring tide pools and colorful marine life. The foreground is dominated by large, weathered rocks covered in dark purple and black mussels or barnacles. Clear, shallow tide pools reflect the sky and surrounding rocks, creating a mirror-like effect. The rocks are a muted green and gray, and the tide pools contain brown seaweed and small pebbles. In the background, a distant rock formation rises from the ocean, partially obscured by a light blue sky with scattered clouds. The overall composition suggests a rugged and natural coastal environment.",
